hiveArticle.title: Color Challenge - Friday Blue - Blue Sky
hiveArticle.body:
My today's post about the Color Challenge is a Blue Sky. There is every detail about this picture and I love watching it again and again. It was the time of sunset where the clouds were amazing, the rays of the sun were easily visible and also the Birds. 

![IMG_20171225_174037.jpg](https://steemitimages.com/DQmXvoh2BNwmExJm6oCNH28L4JKERxjRYTfHtBzMvgDfk6o/IMG_20171225_174037.jpg)

<hr>

### Camera : Nokia 6
